Sentencas: The electrode behaviour of strontium (Sr)-doped LaMnO3 (LSM) electrodes is investigated by an electrochemical impedance spectroscopy technique over the temperature range 850-1000 degreesC and the oxygen partial pressure range 0.01-0.21 atm.
Titulo: Electrode behaviour at (La,Sr)MnO3/Y2O3-ZrO2 interface by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy

Sentencas: The electrodes are screen-printed on 50 mm x 50 mm 3 mol% Y2O3-ZrO2 electrolyte cells with an electrode surface area of 10 cm(2).
Titulo: Electrode behaviour at (La,Sr)MnO3/Y2O3-ZrO2 interface by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy

Sentencas: The impedance responses show two separable arcs and are analysed in terms of two different equivalent circuits with comparable information on the electrode processes at high and low frequencies.
Titulo: Electrode behaviour at (La,Sr)MnO3/Y2O3-ZrO2 interface by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy

Sentencas: The electrode process associated with the high-frequency arc is essentially independent of O-2 partial pressure with an activation energy of similar to74 kJ mol(-1), while that at the low-frequency arc has an activation energy of similar to202 kJ mol(-1) and a reaction order with respect to O-2 partial pressure of similar to0.5 at low temperatures and similar to0.85 at high temperatures.
Titulo: Electrode behaviour at (La,Sr)MnO3/Y2O3-ZrO2 interface by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy

Sentencas: The electrode processes associated with the low- and high-frequency arcs are discussed.
Titulo: Electrode behaviour at (La,Sr)MnO3/Y2O3-ZrO2 interface by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy
